1 (6) money transferred from the Public Service Commission under §
2 7–207.2(d)(3) of the Public Utilities Article; and
3 (7) money distributed under § 2–614.1 of the Tax – General Article.
4 (f) The Administration shall use the Fund:
5 (13) notwithstanding subsection (g) of this section, to pay costs associated
6 with the Air and Radiation Administration within the Department of the Environment;
7 [and]
8 (14) TO AWARD BIDS FOR RENEWABLE ENERGY GENERATION
9 PROJECTS UNDER § 9–20E–02 OF THIS TITLE; AND
10 [(14)] (15) to pay the expenses of the Program.
11 [(g–1) Proceeds received by the Fund from compliance fees under § 7–705(b)(2)(i)2 of
