20 energy relief refund”.
21 (iii) An electric company awarded a grant under this paragraph:
22 1. may not retain any of the grant funds to cover overhead
23 expenses; and
24 2. shall provide all of the grant funds to residential
25 distribution customers.
26 (iv) The process under subparagraphs (i) and (ii) of this paragraph
27 related to the refunding or crediting of amounts to residential distribution customers shall
28 be directed and overseen by the Commission.
